org.kepler.gui

Class SubsetWorkflowOutlineTreeModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • ptolemy.vergil.tree.EntityTreeModel
      • ptolemy.vergil.tree.ClassAndEntityTreeModel

          • org.kepler.gui.SubsetWorkflowOutlineTreeModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.swing.tree.TreeModel

    public class SubsetWorkflowOutlineTreeModel
extends WorkflowOutlineTreeModel
    A tree model that can display a subset of a workflow. Use addToSubset() to select which NamedObjs are in the tree, and then call showSubset() to activate.
    Author:
    Daniel Crawl
